      protected GeneralisableNorms LIONNormRefiner.getGeneralisableNorms(Norm normA, Norm normB, int genStep)
      Given two norms Returns the generalisable norms normA and normB, it performs the following operations: it computes the intersection between norms A and B; if the predicates of both norms are equal but K=genStep predicates, then it computes their generalisable norms.
